LinkedIn profile scraper to mailing list database via QR code reader

Telegram, Uniqode, LinkedIn, Google Sheets, Google Docs

99fold | matt@99foldai.com | @99foldai

napkin script

Get LinkedIn profile data by scanning the QR code from a persons LinkedIn profile with your phone (Telegram bot) to update your database (Airtable, Clickup, Google Sheets), auto draft a personalised email/doc with your own copy/CTA, and save to the cloud (Clickup, Notion, Google Drive).

Summary
